{"tid":1833702,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩宣布關閉北韓邊界禁止外國遊客入境  防堵武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-01-22T04:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T14:25:19.000Z","uid":66271,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"88db2a89acba2aeb3bf8d6a2cf6a0d657f5ff7b3","tid":1833702,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aefimagesnew/aef_image/2019-12-29t214504z_1646842140_rc295e9y3d3s_rtrmadp_3_northkorea-politics.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faefimagesnew%2Faef_image%2F2019-12-29t214504z_1646842140_rc295e9y3d3s_rtrmadp_3_northkorea-politics.jpg&h=d7af77f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎確診病例突破300起，鄰國北韓憂心疫情蔓延，領導人金正恩宣布自周三（22日）起關閉邊境，禁止外國遊客入境。<br />\n<br />\n總部位於中國的「Young Pioneer Tours」冒險旅遊公司在其網站發布聲明，指北韓政府為防範新型冠狀病毒，自周三起暫時對外國遊客關閉邊境。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日星報》報導，前往北韓的絕大部份遊客都來自中國，在美國對其實施嚴厲制裁的情況下，中國遊客對金氏政權是股助力。"},{"pid":"4c0a226bb7da5a146062bb7116964b8d8b374b74","tid":1833702,"uid":345562,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:34:56.000Z","msg":"竟然有羨慕北韓嘅一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84cea10384c352193177d19fdda02deafe97bd5","tid":1833702,"uid":58453,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"北韓或成為亞洲發達國家之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3af17395a38ea0fffd53282ef50f13a87d7570","tid":1833702,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"堆北韓團  全部死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97776df43a61218c3efc8e44cdb02c1f18f4362","tid":1833702,"uid":2